displayName.text: Shri Rani Bhatiyani Mandir Sansthan, Jasol

text.text: Rani Bhatiyani temple is a famous temple in Jasol. She is considered as Rajput princess who attained diety state. The temple is beautifully made and campus is well maintained. Mata bhatiyani is the clan diety of Manganiar musicians which is the famous community of bards. Many Manganiar singer- musician couples are found sitting at various places in temple and singing melodies in praise of goddess.

The temple trust committee management is very good, but I would like to suggest a complaint to the guest house trust committee, that the behavior of your staff on duty in the guest house is not good at all, especially with women and children. Who come to the temple for darshan. And if you have some rules and regulations, then you should write them on rule plates at various places. Do not insult anyone directly.
